00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:49.540
hey

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:51.260
what are you thinking?

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:55.360
Japanese or not, their lives are valuable too!

00:01:55.940 --> 00:01:58.360
that's not something to be embarrassed.

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:02.200
I'm sure I've done the same if it was me.

00:02:03.080 --> 00:02:05.760
