So it that the reason for your wealth?

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:32.620
Did those Japanese rewarded you?

00:02:33.320 --> 00:02:35.640
Ah, hehehe no..

00:02:35.780 --> 00:02:37.340
I'm embarrassed because...

00:02:37.460 --> 00:02:39.820
The reason why I still have enough cash is..

00:02:40.100 --> 00:02:40.720
because..

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:43.940
